quran[16]{c,v,t}:
  15,16,"Gom…óii men wa…óii koode maw…óe ka kammu, …óe yim…ìe …ìen …óoworta e …óalle ma…ì…ìe, ka ni…ìe njorndi e ka maayo. Men wa…óaniri-…óe …ìen ndaaroo…ìe …óe fii yo …ìe dallinor…óe e kattal Alla ngal."
  15,17,"Men reeniri kammu ngun e kala seytaane riiwaa…óo e yurmeende Alla."
  15,18,"Si wanaa on he…óitanii…óo majannde dental ngal, hoodere jalbunde jokkita ngii, nde sumaa ngii."
  15,19,"Leydi ndin, Men weerti ndi ka yim…ìe …ìen daakoo, Men wa…ói e mayri pelle tabitu…óe fii wata ndi yergu e ma…ì…ìe. Men fu…óini e mayri noone kala e pu…ói, kon ko e…ì…ìaa happiraa hikma."
  15,20,"Men wa…óani on ka leydi ton, onon yim…ìe …ìen, ko wuuriron, immorde e √±aametee e njaram, fotde hi…óon e nguurndam aduna. Men wa…óani …ìen …ìe on arsikataa ka yim…ìe e ka kulle kadi ko …ìe wuurira."
  15,21,"Hunnde alaa nde yim…ìe e daabeeji …óin nafitorta, si wanaa Me…óen hattani woodingol nde ko …ìe nafitora. Men woodinaali kadi e nden huunde, si wanaa e e…ì…ìoore happaande yahdunde e √±en∆¥al e muy…óe Amen."
  15,22,"Men wurti keneeli …óin hawrondirooji e duule; Men jippiniri …óen duule to…ìo, Men yarniri on ndiyam to…ìo. Wonaa onon …ìee yim…ìe woni ko mari …óam ndiyam ka leydi, fii ko wona …ìulli e can…ói, ko Alla woni ko mari …óam ton."
  15,23,"Ko Menen kadi woni wuurnitiroo…ìe maay…ìe tagu- gol e waaseede, immintinoya …ìe …ìaawo maayde, Men wuurnita kadi maay…ìe si laje ma…ì…ìe timmii. Ko Menen woni heddotoo…ìe rona leydi ndin e ko woni e mayri."
  15,24,"Gom…óii Men anndii adii…ìe mon jibineede e maa-yoo…ìe, Men anndii kadi sakkitotoo…ìe e mun. Hunnde e …óum suu…óaaki Men."
  15,25,"Pellet, Joomi maa an Nulaa…óo, ko Kanko moo…ìoy- ta …ìe denndaangal √ëalnde Darngal, fii yo O yo…ìu mo∆¥∆¥in…óo on e bonnu…óo on. Kanko ko O √ëee√±u…óo e toppitagol Mo ngol, Anndu…óo Mo huunde suu…óaaki …óum."
  15,26,"Gom…óii Men tagirii Aadama e mbullaari yoorundi wa…óayndi hito si tappaama, ndin ko …ìaleeri waylorndi sabu nee…ìugol waalagol ndi."
  15,27,"Men tagiri baaba jinnaaji …óin ko adii tageede Aadama (yo o his) e yiite ooyunge."
  15,28,"Janto an Nulaa…óo, tuma nde Joomi maa dalannoo Malaa'ika'en e Ibuliisa wonndunoo…óo e ma…ì…ìe: Min Mi tagay …ìanndinke immorde e loopal yooru- yongal, wa…óayngal hito si tappaama, …ìalewal waylotoongal balangol."
  15,29,"Si Mi fotndindirii mo, Mi timminii tagugol mo, haray ko yo on suuyiran mo …óoftagol yamiroore Am e hiwraade mo."
  15,30,"Malaa'ika'en …óoftii yamiroore Joomi ma…ì…ìe, …ìe sujji …ìe fow ma…ì…ìe."
  15,31,"Ibuliisa kan -wonndunoo…óo e Malaa'ika'en kono mo jeyaaka e ma…ì…ìe- ha…óitii sujjanngol Aadama wonndude e Malaa'ika'en."